ditional physical phenomena (e.g. primordial gas bulk flows, unknown\nprimordial popIII stellar mass function, etc.) that have similar or stronger\nimpact on the behaviour of the baryons.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Mar 2011 14:47:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Apr 2011 18:43:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
